---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Accueil" description="BE-ELEC - Électricien professionnel à Bruxelles. Dépannage urgent 24/7, installation électrique, mise en conformité RGIE.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 hero-pattern"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy via-navy to-navy/80 z-10"></div>
    <div class="relative z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left mb-12 md:mb-0">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-bold mb-6 border border-primary/30">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-ping"></span>
          DISPONIBLE MAINTENANT
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Urgence Électrique <br/>
          <span class="text-primary">24/7 à Bruxelles</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto md:mx-0">
          Intervention rapide en moins de 45 minutes pour vos pannes, installations et mises en conformité. Électriciens agréés et expérimentés.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
          <a href="tel:+32470000000" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-navy text-lg font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(253,186,18,0.4)] transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
            <span class="material-icons">call</span>
            Appeler Maintenant
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-lg font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl border border-white/20 transition-all">
            Demander un devis
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative h-[400px] md:h-[500px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-navy-light/50">
        <img alt="Électricien professionnel au travail" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC8wrs8t-IQKlkTIV25wgeygC-QuFjVThkN7YJp151bzlPu6Hhn-uF5CKyIRN_Ewz2pbmHWwUoEEcOLkQKZD1E5bUfgs1YRDCmuA_ZDkgu53HrNx9CaGksUtFK_AvjuYtW22XZgn0eRgjx5hxdTlJ5m9BrTCuZW9QHC48XVzr9it0L_FlzzFrv-yMBV4Yy6XEAmIeuegjVVBgRSRnl5fUNq06lvIlbGhGDBh_Hz4iTOcRIFGg29X8bZwvFQPqKgi0vOh2xt_V_Fqek" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-navy via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/20 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="bg-green-500 rounded-full p-2">
            <span class="material-icons text-white">verified_user</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-bold">Techniciens Agréés</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Certification RGIE</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="bg-navy-light border-y border-white/5 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">15+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Années d'Expérience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">2k+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Clients Satisfaits</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">45m</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Temps Moyen</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Disponibilité</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pourquoi nous choisir -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Pourquoi nous choisir ?</h2>
        <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-b-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <span class="material-icons text-3xl text-primary">timer</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-3">Intervention Rapide</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm">Nous arrivons chez vous en moins de 45 minutes pour les urgences critiques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-b-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <span class="material-icons text-3xl text-primary">verified</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-3">Certifié & Agréé</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm">Tous nos électriciens sont certifiés et respectent les normes RGIE en vigueur.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-b-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <span class="material-icons text-3xl text-primary">euro</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-3">Prix Transparents</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm">Devis clair et détaillé avant toute intervention. Pas de surprise sur la facture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-b-4 border-primary hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <span class="material-icons text-3xl text-primary">handshake</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-3">Travail Garanti</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm">Nous garantissons nos réparations et installations pour votre tranquillité d'esprit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-bg-dark bg-pattern">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-12">
        <div>
          <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-2 block">Nos Expertises</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Services Électriques Complets</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/services" class="hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-semibold hover:text-white transition-colors mt-4 md:mt-0">
          Voir tous les services <span class="material-icons text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="group bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-white/5 glow-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <span class="material-icons text-navy text-3xl">bolt</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Dépannage d'Urgence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Coupure de courant, court-circuit ou panne générale. Intervention immédiate 24h/24 et 7j/7.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="text-accent-blue text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">En savoir plus <span class="material-icons text-xs">arrow_forward_ios</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-white/5 glow-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <span class="material-icons text-navy text-3xl">home</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Installation Domestique</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Rénovation électrique complète, ajout de prises, tableaux électriques et câblage neuf.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="text-accent-blue text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">En savoir plus <span class="material-icons text-xs">arrow_forward_ios</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-white/5 glow-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <span class="material-icons text-navy text-3xl">check_circle</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Mise en Conformité</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Préparation aux contrôles, schémas unifilaires et mise aux normes RGIE pour la vente.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="text-accent-blue text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">En savoir plus <span class="material-icons text-xs">arrow_forward_ios</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-white/5 glow-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <span class="material-icons text-navy text-3xl">lightbulb</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Éclairage LED</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Solutions d'éclairage intérieur et extérieur économiques et esthétiques pour votre habitat.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="text-accent-blue text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">En savoir plus <span class="material-icons text-xs">arrow_forward_ios</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-white/5 glow-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <span class="material-icons text-navy text-3xl">router</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Domotique</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Installation de systèmes intelligents pour le contrôle à distance de votre maison.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="text-accent-blue text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">En savoir plus <span class="material-icons text-xs">arrow_forward_ios</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-navy p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-white/5 glow-hover transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <span class="material-icons text-navy text-3xl">electric_car</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Bornes de Recharge</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Installation certifiée de bornes de recharge pour véhicules électriques à domicile.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="text-accent-blue text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">En savoir plus <span class="material-icons text-xs">arrow_forward_ios</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Avis Clients & FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <!-- Avis -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Avis Clients</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white text-navy p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg relative">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-navy font-bold shadow-md">
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">format_quote</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex text-primary mb-3">
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm italic mb-4">"Intervention super rapide un dimanche soir. L'électricien était très professionnel et a résolu notre panne de courant en 20 minutes. Je recommande vivement !"</p>
              <span class="font-bold text-sm">Thomas D. <span class="text-gray-400 font-normal text-xs">- Bruxelles</span></span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white text-navy p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg opacity-90 scale-95 origin-left">
              <div class="flex text-primary mb-3">
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star</span>
                <span class="material-icons text-sm">star_half</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm italic mb-4">"Mise en conformité réalisée avec succès. Le dossier était complet et le contrôle a été validé du premier coup. Merci pour le sérieux."</p>
              <span class="font-bold text-sm">Sarah L. <span class="text-gray-400 font-normal text-xs">- Ixelles</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Questions Fréquentes</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="group bg-navy border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer bg-navy-light text-white font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-colors">
                <span class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-icons text-primary">euro</span>Tarifs d'urgence</span>
                <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 material-icons text-primary text-2xl">expand_more</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-6 bg-navy text-gray-300 border-t border-white/5">
                <p>Nos tarifs d'urgence sont transparents. Un forfait de déplacement et la première heure sont fixes. Une majoration s'applique uniquement pour les interventions de nuit et les week-ends.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group bg-navy border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer bg-navy-light text-white font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-colors">
                <span class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-icons text-primary">event_available</span>Disponibilité week-end</span>
                <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 material-icons text-primary text-2xl">expand_more</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-6 bg-navy text-gray-300 border-t border-white/5">
                <p>Oui, nous sommes disponibles le samedi et le dimanche, ainsi que les jours fériés. Nos équipes de garde assurent une rotation pour garantir une intervention rapide 24h/24 et 7j/7.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group bg-navy border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer bg-navy-light text-white font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-colors">
                <span class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-icons text-primary">verified_user</span>Garanties</span>
                <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 material-icons text-primary text-2xl">expand_more</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-6 bg-navy text-gray-300 border-t border-white/5">
                <p>Toutes nos installations et réparations sont garanties. Nous utilisons uniquement du matériel agréé CE et respectons strictement les normes du RGIE.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-24 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Besoin d'un Électricien ?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10">Ne laissez pas vos problèmes électriques traîner. Nos experts sont prêts à intervenir.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="tel:+32470000000" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-navy font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">
          <span class="material-icons">phone</span>
          Appeler maintenant
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-navy font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors">
          <span class="material-icons">description</span>
          Demander un Devis en ligne
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
